comments: Heart is a nice teacher but her tests are somewhat hard. Everything is based on attendance...

I took her summer course and I really enjoyed it. She was a wonderful teacher and used a lot of case studies to demonstrate points. Her assignments were a fair ammount of work and kind of fun. There were a lot of extra credit opportunities.

Hart was great. I\'d highly recommend the class, interesting and she knows her stuff. Theres a test every week and they aren\'t very difficult and occasionally group. You need to read the text. Final exam was optional! Can be a bit tedious in class at times but was great overall.
SHE IS AWESOME !!the best teacher i ever had !She is willing to help any student who have a problem !!! her tests are easy and her method of teaching is totally simple and clear !!!
